WEBVTT

00:06:28.960 --> 00:06:30.560
to make something very clear.

00:06:31.720 --> 00:06:34.120
The word "midget" is a slur.

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:39.480
It evolved from PT Barnum's era
of circuses and freak shows.

00:06:40.640 --> 00:06:42.360
Society has evolved.

00:06:43.520 --> 00:06:45.040
So should our vocabulary.

00:06:45.840 --> 00:06:48.216
Language is a powerful tool.

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:50.240
It does not just name our society.

00:06:50.720 --> 00:06:52.160
It shapes it.

00:06:52.880 --> 00:06:56.296
I am incredibly proud
to be a little person,

00:06:56.320 --> 00:06:59.576
to have inherited
the condition of achondroplasia.

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:01.840
But I am most proud to be Sinead.